Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:06.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}光る　宝石の欠片あつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:13.08,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}両手広げれば青く輝くの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:19.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}やけに眩しくて　瞳閉じたの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:26.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}触れた唇　遠い日の記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:32.90,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}さりげない優しさでも惑わずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:40.07,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}運命だって諦めずに変えてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:47.04,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}翼を広げて　手と手を取り合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:53.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}雲の上さえ歩ける気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:03:00.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\pos(283,0)\fs10\fsp3}いま
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:03:00.40,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あなたのいる現在　耐え難い過去もない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:07.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}無数の光から君を　導く
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:06.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}收集著閃光的寶石碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:13.08,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}攤開雙手  那輝煌的群青
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:19.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}是如此的耀眼  我緊閉雙瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:26.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}輕撫紅唇  遙遠的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:32.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不被那不經意間的溫柔所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:40.07,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}縱使命中注定  亦從不放棄  將其改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:47.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}若攜君手  振翅翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:53.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}則可漫步雲巔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:03:00.40,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}在有你的今日裡  難熬的過往亦化作煙塵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:07.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}在無數的光輝中指引著你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:23:01.38,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}雨降るバスでお出かけしても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.35,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あなたは不機嫌なままで歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:15.08,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ご機嫌とると笑顔になるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:21.90,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}理想の世界を創っていける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:25.26,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}夢の中の出来事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:29.05,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不満ばかりを　言って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:31.49,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}妄想のロマンス
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:36.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}私は好きだけど！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:40.60,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}おとぎ話の中でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:44.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}永遠なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:50.13,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}お姫様だってカンカンよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:54.52,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}おとぎ話の１ページ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:57.93,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}新しいページを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:24:05.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}めくれるのは　（そう）あなた
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:23:01.38,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}細雨紛紛  縱使乘巴士出行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.35,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}你  仍舊是一臉不悅  埋頭行路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:15.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}逢迎你心  便能綻開笑顏？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:21.90,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}理想之鄉  即可著手雕塑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:29.05,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}夢中故事  雖說滿腹牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:36.16,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}但我  卻中意於  那妄想的浪漫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:44.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}從來就沒有什麼永恆  即便是在傳說裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:50.13,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}就算是公主  也會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:57.93,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}而那翻開傳說的篇章  那嶄新的篇章的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:24:05.17,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}是的  便是你了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------INJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:22.06,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}かけがえのない　星たちを見つめ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:27.35,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}失うことない　輝きでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:33.81,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}形あるもの　いつかは壊れる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:39.16,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}怖がらないで　踏み出そうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:50.17,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}聞こえている　星の言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:22:07.11,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}さざなみの様に浴びて　僕らは君たちとゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:15.23,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}これから先のこの未来　輝いている扉開け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:20.92,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}あなたの胸に飛び込んでゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:26.92,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}いつまで続くぬくもりを　忘れずにいて永遠に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:33.42,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}続く未来ずっと
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------INCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:22.06,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}凝望著  那無可替代的點點繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:27.35,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}縱使是些許的光芒  亦不曾褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:33.81,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}有形之物  終究歸於塵土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:39.16,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}但不必畏懼  請向前邁步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:50.17,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我能聽見  那群星的絮語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:22:07.11,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}縈迴耳際  恍若漣漪  前途無盡  但有你我同路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:15.23,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}遠方未來  無限光輝  漸次展開  徐徐大幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:20.92,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我  決定飛入你的胸懷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:26.92,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}這永不逝去的溫暖  我絕不忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:33.42,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}直至明天的旅途
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…  多重人格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  這個遊戲的主角就有多重人格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是羽田吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一先問問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是「其實我只是做夢睡傻了」這樣說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.49,0:00:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的會相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比較難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我在這三年裡也幾次會碰到這樣的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說  我也是羽田名義上的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名義上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也不想說得這麼輕率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為我比起站在那裡的某人更能理解羽田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放心吧  我不會對你做什麼」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「但請你先跟我詳細說說」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.47,0:00:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得這麼討人厭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想互相幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相幫助？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  某種程度上說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有著跟他相同的境遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於這個的來龍去脈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等你說完了我再告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先有個小小的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(332,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事請對鷹志君保密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.10,0:01:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他完全不知道他自己裡面還有我們這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓他一下子知道了真相  你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.44,0:01:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能向天神發誓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對已經不在此世的弟弟發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就重新自我介紹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是千歲鷲介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eagle的鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碇矢長介的介  鷲介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱鷲介大濕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲鷲介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TITLE-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:23.01,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中小鹿亂撞
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就給說出去了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  順勢就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少給我扯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼幾下功夫就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到底為了什麼費神至今啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  那好像是鷹志的女朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼可能有女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是本人聽見了  可會受打擊的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人才是  怎麼樣啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近不是有什麼幹得挺起勁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有心上人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你  跟那個頭上有星星標記的女人怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟日和子才沒有這樣的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是職場上的前輩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那個女人叫日和子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣  無論如何也要把隼人的心上人的名字問出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒這號人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我嘛  其實還是有的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當這是修學旅行的夜晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  別給我轉移話題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在問你幹嘛這麼兩三下功夫就把我們的秘密說出去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我們也沒多少時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(388,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.74,0:04:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香同學也說想幫鷹志君一把
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也有不少事要解決呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  關於咱倆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是像以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互不干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(359,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  話說那個鷹志呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在格雷塔加爾德那沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:04:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回去得還真夠久的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的早飯吃什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩  你還記得我不喜歡吃蘆筍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外咖哩飯  雖然只是昨天的剩飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖哩放一個晚上會更好吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.51,0:05:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(297,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹志君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子  這次好像去得比較久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  我跟隼人君會跟進的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有千歲先生跟成田先生…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…伊丹先生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊丹…啊  伽樓羅君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該不會再出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說  他這危險的傢伙不出來才是造福大眾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也碰到過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是哥哥  也不是那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種各樣的人  不知不覺地就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧？還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(274,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演得像鷹志君一樣客氣一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客氣一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你也是一個班的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯吃麵包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  食堂人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在路上買的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你也來一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越過癮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽田同學  羽田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…誰來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊  我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小京啊  小京  山科京啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山科同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小京太感激了  太感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感動得全山科都要哭出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到羽田同學這麼大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向你搭話真是做得太對了  不愧是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也是第一次  心裡也七上八下的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽田同學對我這麼溫柔真是太讓人高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是少女啊  清純的少女啊  還是處女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在已經是一個女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(229,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹志君到底幹了什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是想起來就已經不能自已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡也睡不著  睜著眼睛就這麼過了一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的雖然不行  但是橙色的更加禁止使用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過即便這樣還是洗不去羽田同學的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體發熱  發熱  不能自已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就做了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚥口水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相性占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一個占卜都棒極了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是花  還是星星  還是動物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連龜殼占卜也好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人就把這對話持續了這麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以引以為傲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}註：miyako=京
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽田君你是made in miyako的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很久沒露出本性說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不用就著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(76,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹志君也真是的  我還以為他過著本分健全的學生生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到除了明日香同學之外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這麼多要提防的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什麼鷲鷲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是找我有什麼事就請叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷲之介？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(308,323)\fs20}washi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷲介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(308,323)\fs20}washi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(376,323)\fs20}shuu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫作鷲讀作鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,323)\fs20}shuu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷲之介？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒有之了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(308,323)\fs20}washi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷲介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛又繞回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝各位捧場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(414,323)\fs20}washi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  怎麼今天一直都是鷲介啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能換羽田君出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(279,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這次鷹志君這次不知怎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲遲都不回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲一天只能玩一個小時啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他什麼時候才回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話想跟羽田君說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(438,323)\fs20}takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒昧  請把我當成羽田鷹志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵  老娘一巴掌扇中你腦袋把你抽暈過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會就換回來了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  怎麼回事  這個暴力的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是我的回合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這身打扮讓人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  這個時間的千歲鷲介才是真正的千歲鷲介
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也濕濕地上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲先生  你真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  借大家一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事要趁現在說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信大家也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾天後就是平安夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…店長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女老少普天同慶的神聖夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是對我們飲食業來說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是決戰之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  我們亞歷山大為了吸引更多的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備了秘密兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是她們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店專屬idol unit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alex 2的2位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是Alex 2
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英里里  太好了  我們終於能出道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭嘛  紀奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候偶像更應該微笑著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖別哭  紀奈子妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱兩首來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幫人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後二位將作為本店的形象代表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從事本店各種推銷活動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安夜當日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要在店內舉行演唱會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英里里  守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要忙起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀奈子會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長  我有個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了  製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘記了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店還有另一顆鑽石的原石…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲鷲介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要當偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近這種的還是有人需要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別扔東西啊  被打中的地方好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫peace
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家店子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  紀奈子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是為了備考  才辭掉工作的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天跑這兒玩的話  不就沒意義了不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢就是  我今天來這兒也是帶了這玩意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊  今天發售的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是全文登載了哦  千歲君你寫的日和子的書評
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  在這兒  就是這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我看看  是什麼內容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要為這部作品打一個比方的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就恰似在景區步道上閒庭信步一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從淡然的筆觸中流露出的諸多情景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然而然  漸次滲出的種種情緒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要  人家會害羞的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人當面朗讀自己寫的文章什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然作者在這裡可能是寫得有點不太平易近人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可總有一天  讀者們也應該會理解其文中的深意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千歲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很會誇人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想人們讀了這篇介紹文  應該都會想去讀這本書的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛  就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要讀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過實際讀完以後  大概是會失望的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任誰也不會喜歡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓一個隱居山林的老爺子來當主角
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛  就是這樣才好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2\fsp-1}該怎麼說呢  就像是這樣  宛如魷魚乾一樣  值得讓人反覆咀嚼回味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀奈子你怎麼看？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  之前那本我覺得倒是相當不錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過實話實說  這回這本確實是有點不怎麼樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實  就算是讓爺爺輩的人來當主角  也不是不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是描寫得一方面是太沒有說服力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面  也是因為太年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以對老人的認識  也就只停留在印象層面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是沒辦法的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}註：細川玉木是日和子的筆名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,細川玉木老師她呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一個正值青春年少的少女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種年紀輕輕  卻又想挑戰新境界的創作欲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是應該給予肯定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果單憑創作欲  書就能賣得動的話  也就沒那麼多事兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上不是根本賣不動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這第二部作品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要早知是這樣  一開始就不該打腫臉充胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是走老路  寫自己拿手的少女戀愛小說不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣才更受人追捧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  日和…  同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…  全聽見了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的感想  我以後執筆的時候  會加以參考的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…  謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又裝起這副態度了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這副態度」是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  我覺得以前的玉木明顯更可愛一點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日和子小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然確實是有一些地方  讓人很在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過包括這一些在內
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很喜歡這部名叫「八十八歲壽辰」的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}註：米字拆開寫  即為八十八  因此日本將八十八歲大壽  稱作「米壽」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說英里同學你啊…  其實也沒必要說得那麼尖銳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對她的話  還是像這樣直截了當地挑明了的好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過英里同學  不管怎麼說  你還是讀的相當仔細的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把日和同學她寫的書
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這年代了  你們兩個居然還沒有手機  這也太離譜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  亞衣  冷靜  冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼啊  突然這麼弄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是到頭來沒意思的話  當心我一拳飛了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  又不是找你  我找的是小鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來  快來  小鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輛  跟小鳴你的自行車  不是挺像的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  確實是紅色的沒錯  但還是有一點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  沒找對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的自行車  造型稍微有點特別
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座位的後面加裝了一個靠背
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是改裝靠背嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  為什麼連你們也集體出動  幫她找自行車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  你說什麼啊  這也太過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友有難  挺身相助  這不是理所當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  也因為我們是這座城市的自警團
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳木原火鳥團的緣故啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi stop  稍等稍等  please
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a time please？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…  好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣的話  也算上我們一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連你們也來摻上一腳？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜  冷靜  長毛君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不是想來給你們添亂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  我們這是想來還禮的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對  就是你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吧沒錯吧？  成田隼人君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個Fucking大司教給一拳打飛的  就是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那事兒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他瘋成那樣  給我們也添了不少麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將天譴降與那已然墮落不堪的妖人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方才是將我們引向天堂的傳教士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  成田君超級無敵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以叫你聲大哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗶哩嗶哩嗶哩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我們也來幫忙找自行車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了回報你的英雄行為
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是大哥你就放一百個心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那邊的pretty girl們一起好好樂樂才是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是搞什麼名堂啊  他們這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了吧  和君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不能等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須趕快通知LR他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就是看那幫人和我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪邊先找到小鳴的自行車了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦也  YFB對R-Wing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二次「世界大戰」  就此爆發了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好燃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個  先在小春薄餅店那邊等著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了馬上聯繫你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bye bye~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  還是先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去小春姐那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的沒問題嗎  皇帝？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有成員全部出動  去找小鳴的自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有什麼不好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又能夠打發時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  那事情可還真有點大條了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說那些傢伙是真閒得慌呢  還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起沒事到處亂來  還是正常許多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能找到的  鳴的自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝啦  愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  話說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非那輛自行車不可嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有去新買一輛的選項嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴格說來  比起自行車本身  我更想找回籃子裡的東西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面放了什麼特別重要的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是大家說的BP機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,POCKET BELL…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有搞錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:19:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是從小到大一直在用BP機的死忠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真復古啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我以前也經常靠這玩意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過該是時候買部手機了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒朋友  所以也就沒有發簡訊的對象啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部呼叫器  是媽媽送給我的禮物…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因為家庭原因  媽媽並沒有和我住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2\fsp-1}對於我  除了這呼叫器的號碼  我媽媽應該不知道其他的聯絡手段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…  呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德拉  一定要找到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子的自行車  還有呼叫器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也拜託下看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該很快就會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果調動國家的力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  別搞成國際問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  敵人是誰  這一點很清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是大規模犯罪組織的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾經見過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一群人把停在吉姆的攤子前面的自行車們全部搬上卡車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.55,0:20:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後統統拖走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個不是啦  不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才不是什麼犯罪組織呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區政府派來的城管啦  那些人是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們這是打著美化環境的旗號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒收車站前面亂停亂放的自行車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像偶爾也真在這麼搞…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴啊  我想你應該是第一時間就去區政府那邊問了的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的啦  我還是頭一回聽說  區政府還在兼做這事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我是歸僑子女啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬不？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  這太陽也太刺眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想幹架嗎  這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  還真是新奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  哪兒新奇啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:21:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時間還能和隼人先生你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  說起來還真是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是這輛！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的自行車啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  話說回來  我們好像忘了聯繫他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這群臭烏鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們才是呢  是時候該認輸了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  我們還能再戰十年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸你個頭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的呼叫器…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勞你幫我找了這麼長的時間  真是謝謝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  也沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我說  你等等啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是怎麼啦  人家可是很在意的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來了什麼消息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你猜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.75,0:22:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到市中心為止  咱們來比一比誰快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我說  你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十一路怎麼可能跑得過兩輪車嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是慢性運動不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人先生你也買輛自行車嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.16,0:22:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  下回要不要大家一起去玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫上小亞衣和小春姐還有愛麗絲她們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  叫你等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…  求你讓我喘口氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  隼人先生你想去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  隨便啦  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看著辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.82,0:22:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  心中小鹿亂撞！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:25.03,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(471,0)}{\bord1}次回  請一直當我的粉絲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  大家好  我已經掛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.23,0:24:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DJ禿鷲  今天也在第十八層地獄絕讚死亡中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.03,0:24:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明早就掛了  但還是在說個不停的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.80,0:24:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只有禿鷲我了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.75,0:24:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快向禿鷲老師我發來唁電吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.28,0:24:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掃墓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.23,0:24:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對會來的吧？


